com.appboy.models.push

Class BrazeNotificationPayload

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appboy.models.push.BrazeNotificationPayload

  • public class BrazeNotificationPayload
extends java.lang.Object
    A convenience class for parsing the Braze Notification payload. Values are not lazy-loaded and are computed from the input arguments on each constructor call.

    Null return values for methods, such as on getCustomNotificationId() are the result of that key either not existing in the original push payload or not being in the proper expected format.

      • getAttachedAppboyExtras

        public static android.os.Bundle getAttachedAppboyExtras(android.os.Bundle notificationExtras)
        Get the extras Bundle from the notification extras or an empty bundle.
        Parameters:
        notificationExtras - Notification extras.
        Returns:
        Returns the Braze extras Bundle from the notification extras. Amazon ADM recursively flattens all JSON messages, so for Amazon devices we just return a copy of the original bundle.
